<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0916004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0916004">論本＝卷【甲】</note>
<note n="0916005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0916005">此下甲本有中大雲寺沙門圓暉述，分別業品第四之六，十七字</note>
<note n="0917001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0917001">〔時〕－【甲】</note>
<note n="0917002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0917002">多＝受【甲】</note>
<note n="0917003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0917003">〔行〕－【甲】</note>
